Package: translateR
Title: Bindings for the Google and Microsoft Translation APIs
Version: 2.0
Date: 2018-01-23
Author: Christopher Lucas, Dustin Tingley, and Vasundhara Dehiya
Maintainer: Christopher Lucas <christopher.lucas@wustl.edu>
Description: Provides easy access to the Google and Microsoft APIs. The 
	package is easy to use with the related R package "stm" for the estimation of 
	multilingual topic models.
Imports: RJSONIO,RCurl,parallel,httr,utils
License: GPL-3

